description: Serial Number of the DKC.
variables.name: HDS9900MIB::trapCommandSerialNumber

description: Name of manager who has lock.
variables.name: HDS9900MIB::trapCommandManagerName

description: Request Command.
Value Mean
1 Request to refresh the configuration information.
2 Request to set the LUNM/LUSE configuration.
3 Request to set the LUN Security configuration.
4 Request to get the exclusive lock.
5 Request to free the exclusive lock.
6 Request to check the health.
7 Request to set the CVS configuration.
8 Request to set the DCR configuration.
9 Request to set the HIHSM configuration.
variables.name: HDS9900MIB::trapCommandKind

description: Status of Requested Command.
Value Mean
1 Normal state. (The command ended normally.)
2 Command execution request. (now executing.)
other Abnormal state (Error occurred).
